  "original_title": "Pusswedilla\u2019s take on Ranil speech",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Pusswedilla\u2019s take on Ranil speech",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "My dear Acting President Wikrama Nikamsinghe From National List to Coconut Trees and now to the Presidency. What you have achieved with less than 30,000 votes is quite amazing!",
        "You gave a speech to the nation upon assumption of the Presidency (Acting) till Parliament selects a new one (or re-appoints you. Let\u2019s see, I haven\u2019t decided yet)",
        "1. Use a teleprompter. Or wear your spectacles. Carrying massive cue cards when you are addressing the nation feels a little like a nursery time show-and-tell",
        "2. You have stopped the usage of the term \u201cHis Excellency\u201d that is a good move. I don\u2019t think many people were planning on calling you \u201cExcellency\u201d anyway",
        "3. You said that it is time for people to move on from Party politics and join hands. I couldn\u2019t help but smile at how ironic and moronic that statement was",
        "4. You have said that the Presidential flag is olso not needed and the nation needs only one flag. The nation olways had only one flag. The President\u2019s flag was never in competition with the National one. Olso, this one-nation-one-anything nonsense has a bad ring to it",
        "Anyway, good luck for the next week. A long time ago, I gave you a smoll replica of my chair and said that you can sit on it for as long as you like. Even to my surprise you have managed to wriggle yourself onto the real chair. Your Uncle Dickie must be proud."
      ],
